<subSubSection lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="342" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,1662,2013]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1807,1833]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Naidu, K. V. &amp; Rao, G. C." box="[322,556,1807,1833]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" pagination="169" refId="ref12873" refString="Naidu, K. V. &amp; Rao, G. C. (2004) Gastrotricha. In: Fauna of India and the adjacent countries. Zoological Survey of India, Kol- kata, pp. 169." type="book chapter" year="2004">Naidu &amp; Rao (2004)</bibRefCitation>
, following 
<bibRefCitation author="Schwank, P." box="[684,887,1807,1833]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" pagination="1 - 262" refId="ref13700" refString="Schwank, P. (1990) Gastrotricha. In: Braur, A., Schwoerbel, J. &amp; Zwick, P. (Eds.), Susswasser Fauna von Mitteleuropa. Band 3. Heft 1. 2. Gastrotricha und Nemertini. Gustav Fischer Verlag, Stuttgart and Jenai, pp. i - xvi + 1 - 262." type="book chapter" year="1990">Schwank’s (1990)</bibRefCitation>
classification indicate several species as belonging to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Schwank, 1990-01" authorityName="Schwank" authorityYear="1990" box="[382,538,1843,1869]" class="Not" family="Chaetonotidae" genus="Euichthydium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chaetonotida" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" phylum="Gastrotricha" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[382,538,1843,1869]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Euichthydium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, as explained by 
<bibRefCitation author="Kanneby, T. &amp; Todaro, M. A. &amp; Jondelius, U." box="[858,1111,1842,1869]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" pagination="26 - 46" refId="ref12131" refString="Kanneby, T., Todaro, M. A. &amp; Jondelius, U. (2009) One new species and records of Ichthydium Ehrenberg, 1830 (Gastrotricha: Chaetonotida) from Sweden with a key to the genus. Zootaxa, 2278 (1), 26 - 46. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2278.1.2" type="journal article" year="2009">
Kånneby 
<emphasis box="[968,1019,1843,1869]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">et al</emphasis>
. (2009)
</bibRefCitation>
, the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Schwank, 1990" authorityName="Schwank" authorityYear="1990" class="Not" family="Chaetonotidae" genus="Euichthydium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chaetonotida" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" phylum="Gastrotricha" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1281,1437,1843,1869]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Euichthydium</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Schwank, P." box="[151,325,1879,1905]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" pagination="1 - 262" refId="ref13700" refString="Schwank, P. (1990) Gastrotricha. In: Braur, A., Schwoerbel, J. &amp; Zwick, P. (Eds.), Susswasser Fauna von Mitteleuropa. Band 3. Heft 1. 2. Gastrotricha und Nemertini. Gustav Fischer Verlag, Stuttgart and Jenai, pp. i - xvi + 1 - 262." type="book chapter" year="1990">Schwank, 1990</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is invalid because it contains the type-species of the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ehrenberg" authorityYear="1830" box="[1008,1134,1879,1905]" family="Chaetonotidae" genus="Ichthydium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chaetonotida" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" phylum="Gastrotricha" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1008,1134,1879,1905]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Ichthydium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, therefore it must bear the same name as the genus.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,1662,2013]" lastBlockId="10.[151,1436,151,249]" lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="342" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Brunson" authorityYear="1950" box="[199,421,1951,1977]" family="Chaetonotidae" genus="Ichthydium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chaetonotida" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" phylum="Gastrotricha" rank="species" species="auritum">
<emphasis box="[199,421,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Ichthydium auritum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was found in 
<collectingCountry box="[578,636,1951,1977]" name="India" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">India</collectingCountry>
twice and both records are from 
<collectingRegion box="[1003,1144,1951,1977]" country="India" name="West Bengal" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">West Bengal</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Sharma, B. K." box="[1158,1311,1951,1977]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" pagination="265 - 267" refId="ref13765" refString="Sharma, B. K. (1980) Taxonomic notes on some freshwater Gastrotricha from West Bengal, India. Hydrobiologia, 70, 265 - 267. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / BF 00016769" type="journal article" year="1980">Sharma 1980</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Sharma B. K. &amp; Sharma S." pageId="9" pageNumber="341" pagination="211 - 215" refId="ref13843" refString="Sharma B. K. &amp; Sharma S. (1990) On some Freshwater Gastrotricha from N. E. Region. Records of the Zoological Survey of India, 86, 211 - 215." type="journal article" year="1990">Sharma &amp; Sharma 1990</bibRefCitation>
). The specimens found match the original description especially in showing the posterior lobes of the head in the form of ear-like flaps. Regarding this latter detail 
<bibRefCitation author="Sharma, B. K." box="[842,1009,151,177]" pageId="10" pageNumber="342" pagination="265 - 267" refId="ref13765" refString="Sharma, B. K. (1980) Taxonomic notes on some freshwater Gastrotricha from West Bengal, India. Hydrobiologia, 70, 265 - 267. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / BF 00016769" type="journal article" year="1980">Sharma (1980)</bibRefCitation>
considered 
<taxonomicName box="[1145,1311,151,177]" family="Chaetonotidae" genus="Ichthydium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chaetonotida" pageId="10" pageNumber="342" phylum="Gastrotricha" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[1145,1271,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="342">Ichthydium</emphasis>
sp.
</taxonomicName>
previously found in 
<collectingRegion box="[252,432,187,213]" country="India" name="Andhra Pradesh" pageId="10" pageNumber="342">Andhra Pradesh</collectingRegion>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Rao, R. K. &amp; Mohan, P. C." box="[475,718,187,213]" pageId="10" pageNumber="342" pagination="45 - 46" refId="ref13387" refString="Rao, R. K. &amp; Mohan, P. C. (1984) Ichthydium auritum Brunson, 1950 (Gastrotricha), a new record for India. Geobios New Report, 3, 45 - 46." type="journal article" year="1984">Rao &amp; Mohan (1984)</bibRefCitation>
to be a different species, whose taxonomic status remains to be established. We agree with Sharma’s hypothesis.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
